The '''True Guild''' was a faction of the [[Bounty Hunters' Guild/Legends|Bounty Hunters' Guild]] during the [[Bounty Hunter Wars]] led by [[Gleed Ontondon]]. It was composed of the elders who had run the Guild and reaped the profits, igniting the resentment of the younger, [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]]-earning members who formed the [[Guild Reform Committee]].

